When I had it as a single file, the DefinitelyTyped linter complained because I was declaring modules, so I split it out. So, I guess I'm not sure how to do what you're requesting and still keep the linter happy.

```
declare module 'viz.js' {
  export = Viz;
}

declare module 'viz.js/full.render.js' {
  export const Module: IModule;
  export function render(instance: IModule, src: string, options: IOptions): string;
}
```

